snippet.title: Amber Heard admits chopping off Johnny Depps finger- shocking new audio !
snippet.description:
Rachael and Kev discuss the latest releases by the Daily Mail in relation to the Amber Heard/Johnny Depp finger cutting incident. 

In this video, they compare and contrast the timelines put forward by Johnny Depp and Amber Heard along with the audio and testimony released by the Daily Mail.


Credit to @winonasrider on twitter for her help on this video.

Due to self isolation this was a difficult video to make and edit, we hope things make sense and we got our points across. #justiceforjohnnydepp 

For more information check out incredibly average on YouTube or @thatbrianfella on twitter 

You can now also check out Johnny Depp on Instagram @johnnydepp and Facebook (https://m.facebook.com/JohnnyDepp/)

Isolation performed by Johnny Depp and Jeff Beck , written by John Lennon - no copyright infringement intended. Licensed to warner music group on behalf of Rhino.  

Please download at https://rhino.lnk.to/isolationAW

#JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp #AmberHeard
